(9, 1, '2018-06-18 05:47:20', '2018-06-18 05:47:20', 'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Accusamus atque commodi error esse non quibusdam sint, soluta. Architecto hic incidunt libero pariatur provident quos voluptas! Commodi, maxime quam? Sit, soluta!', 'Recipe 1', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'recipe-1', '', '', '2018-06-18 09:14:03', '2018-06-18 09:14:03', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wsc/module_A/git/TO6_cms_module/02_cms_module/?post_type=recipe&#038;p=9', 0, 'recipe', '', 0),
